 46	/**
 47	 * ReAct-style agent loop: Think → Act → Observe → repeat until done.
 48	 * Runs on its own thread (implements Runnable). Pushes {@link AgentEvent}
 49	 * instances to a {@link BlockingQueue} consumed by the UI thread.
 50	 *
 51	 * <p>Each iteration applies two-layer context compaction:
 52	 * <ol>
 53	 *   <li>Layer 1 — ToolResultBudget replaces large/stale tool results with previews</li>
 54	 *   <li>Layer 2 — ContextCompactor triggers an LLM summary when tokens exceed 80%</li>
 55	 * </ol>
 56	 */
